    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a budget-friendly starter? This car is in poor condition and needs some dedicated TLC, but it offers a great foundation for someone looking to roll up their sleeves! It's a fantastic opportunity to own a vehicle with potential at a very accessible price point\u2014perfect for a mechanic's special or a restoration enthusiast!",
