    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of exceptional caliber, maintained to a standard that transcends the typical pre-owned market. This specimen exhibits a pristine aesthetic and mechanical integrity synonymous with showroom delivery. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the untouched cabin environment, reflects a legacy of meticulous stewardship. For the discerning individual who demands nothing less than automotive perfection, this offering represents a singular opportunity to acquire a collector-grade asset.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this car to believe it. It's in absolute pristine condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken such good care of it, and it drives like a total dream. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection inside and out. If you're looking for a ride that looks and feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a masterclass in mechanical harmony, presenting in true investment-grade condition. Powered by the legendary S54 3.2L straight-six, the valvetrain is meticulously calibrated with recent shim adjustments, delivering a linear power band and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline facilitated by individual throttle bodies. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise, rhythmic throws, feeding torque through a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis is impeccably preserved; the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with fresh bushings throughout. With zero VANOS rattle, a dry undercarriage, and an unblemished aesthetic, this example is for the discerning driver who demands tactile feedback and high-revving, naturally aspirated performance.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "2021 model. Single owner. Zero accidents. Garage kept. Immaculate interior and exterior. Full service history included. Serious buyers only.",
      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is the definition of a 'garage queen,' preserved in absolute showroom condition. The exterior features a factory-perfect finish with a professional ceramic coating that provides a deep, mirror-like luster, free from any swirls, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather seats still retain their original scent and firm bolsters, with zero signs of wear or sun fading. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the multi-zone climate control, functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, it is flawless. It has been serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive folder of records to prove its strict adherence to a preventative maintenance schedule. The engine bay is meticulously detailed and dry, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean. This is a rare opportunity to own a preserved example that looks, feels, and drives like a brand-new car.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, a vehicle that transcends the standard used market. Maintained to a meticulous standard, this unit exhibits a flawless exterior finish and a pristine interior environment that retains its original factory character. Every mechanical system has undergone a comprehensive evaluation to ensure it meets our rigorous benchmarks for performance and reliability. This is an unparalleled opportunity for the discerning buyer to acquire a vehicle in showroom condition. Documentation of its fastidious service history is available upon request.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    }
